content: Hello Jeyachandran! Thank you for coming in today. I'm Master, the hiring manager for this position. I'll be asking you some technical questions related to your skills and experience. Based on your resume, I'd like to start with a question about your experience as an AI Project Developer at Shine Logics. Can you walk me through your project, "Developed a web app for mock interviews utilizing AI to ask voice-based questions based on uploaded resumes, while students reply in text"? What were some of the challenges you faced during this project, and how did you overcome them?
